summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Mercer Corridor Project; redesignating a portion of two parcels of property owned by the City and needed to construct the Mercer Corridor Project from limited-access highway purposes to general-street purposes; one parcel being a portion of Parcel 40, Block 2, Eden Addition, and the other parcel being a portion of Parcel 57, Block 81, Lake Union Shoreland Addition.
